1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Bug Bunny is an evidence console
for authorized Web research.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
The explicit scope gate records the target,
testing boundary, and authorization.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:15,000
The Safe Web audit captures bounded,
read-only evidence from the live target.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:19,000
Surface Map shows the safe routes
and signals that deserve human review.

5
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:29,000
The same-state IDOR replay proves legitimate access,
then demonstrates victim data exposure.

6
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:37,000
Codex and GPT-5.6 Sol turn collected evidence
into a reproducible, proof-ready report.
